desc: StarBox, Inc. is an ON TIME / ON DEMAND provider of temperature sensitive and industrial packaging products. We specialize in supplying high quality products for the Seafood, Air Freight, Floral, Meat & Poultry, Fresh Produce and Live Tropical Fish industries.
